hopobject.body: I work here zynapse tablet Unlike reports that the IG's office says exonerate an official of suspected wrongdoing, these are investigations that found problems serious enough to merit the official's removal from office or reprimand. They range from poor management to misuse of government money to using office staff as servants to run personal errands.
